@startuml
Digital Watch State Diagram

[*] --> Idle : Initial Transition
Idle --> AdjustTime : Button Pressed

state Idle
...

state AdjustTime
AdjustTime --> HourAdjust : Button Pressed (Hour)
AdjustTime --> MinuteAdjust : Button Pressed (Minute)
AdjustTime --> AlarmHourAdjust : Button Pressed (Alarm Hour)
AdjustTime --> AlarmMinuteAdjust : Button Pressed (Alarm Minute)
...

state OnAlarm
OnAlarm --> RingAlarm : Current Time Matches Alarm Time
OnAlarm --> StopAlarm : Specific Button Pressed
OnAlarm --> Idle : Final Transition
...

state OffAlarm
OffAlarm --> OnAlarm : Alarm Toggled On
...

state LightControl
LightControl --> LightOn : Button Pressed (Light)
LightControl --> LightOff : Button Released (Light)
LightControl --> Idle : Final Transition
@enduml
